Package: HLCaTrace
Title: Reproducible Calcium Imaging Trace Analysis Workflow
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
        "Yiying",
        "Li",
        email = "yiyingli423@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: 
    HLCaTrace is an R package for reproducible calcium imaging trace analysis.
    The package provides workflows for F/F0 normalization, responding cell
    detection, population timecourse summarization, and automated figure
    generation from Fiji/ImageJ-exported fluorescence datasets.
